        "title": "Authentically Fake",
        "text": "I felt pressured to take a swig out of that bottle. I knocked off a star for that. I would have liked some sort of explanation of what the hell was going on. Knocked of \u00bd star for that. But, on reflection, I no longer care that the entire \u201cceremony\u201d was been put on for me. The ceremony might have been fake, but the experience was real. I met a community in a small Ghanian village and got a glimpse into their traditional culture. Through my tourism dollars, I contributed financially to the community. And I made connections. I know those photos will last, though they\u2019ll probably fade before my memories."
